{{zh-forms|[[无]][[法]][[无]][[天]]|[[無法無天]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: wúfǎwútiān
===Etymology===
Literally: no (respect for) law<sup>1</sup> and no (respect for) heaven(ly justice<sup>2</sup>)<br>
<sup>1</sup>[[法]] is short for [[法纪]] (law)<br>
<sup>2</sup>[[天]] is short for [[天理]] (heavenly justice)

===Idiom===
# no respect for law and order; unruly
===Proper noun===
# [[w:American Outlaws|American Outlaws]]

===Derived terms===
*[[和尚打伞，无法无天]]

